  <summary date="2020-07-22T04:00:00Z" status="Introduced in House">No Funds for Apportionment Exclusion Act

This bill prohibits using federal funds to carry out the July 21, 2020, presidential memorandum ordering the exclusion of aliens without legal immigration status from being counted for the purposes of apportioning representation in the House of Representatives following the 2020 census.</summary>
